{"tid":912042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★不爆？】人力資源顧問：明年內地加薪預測達百分之6.5，是大中華區之冠。","createTime":"2018-11-22T11:08:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T22:50:33.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0356e3d9a1e1dddac6c61b7b641a27586237e498","tid":912042,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T11:08:11.000Z","msg":"一間國際人力資源顧問機構分析69個國家和地區，近三百間跨國企業的薪酬數據，預測本港明年加薪百分之4；內地的增幅預測達百分之6.5，是大中華區之冠。  <br />\n<br />\n但若計及預期通脹率，本港的實質薪酬增幅只有百分之1.9，低於亞太區平均數百分之2.7。  調查機構指，本港薪酬水平已高於亞洲大部分地方，因此來年增幅未及一些新興經濟體。雖然鄰近的廣州及深圳薪酬增速較快。但稅率亦較高，機構認為不影響本港吸引人才。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KM03B5x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKM03B5x.png&h=f8fe4233&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QcLOOcd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQcLOOcd.png&h=0f3978e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5bf68574e603839b50efdc9c/?lang=cht\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5bf68574e603839b50efdc9c%2F%3Flang%3Dcht&d=rPtqwKu4L7zNuShv7ENrV49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=0d3a1540\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5bf68574e603839b50efdc9c/?lang=cht</a>"},{"pid":"063dc8944a351cd08abfbda17c98fa98aa1bdee6","tid":912042,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T11:08:27.000Z","msg":"冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"099c23f70e5f732f0ba61c410a3ddabc12a81baf","tid":912042,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T11:09:06.000Z","msg":"調查機構=5毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36da206336a22ff4278de0f51fb891163d09c2f7","tid":912042,"uid":26752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0356e3d9a1e1dddac6c61b7b641a27586237e498","tid":912042,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime